      <pre><code>&lt;p class="lead">This is a lead paragraph.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>This is a regular paragraph.&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="text-small">This is a small paragraph.&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="text-tiny">This is a tiny paragraph.&lt;/p></code></pre>
