  <h3>Text weight</h3>
  <div class="grid-x grid-margin-x">
    <div class="cell large-6">
      <p>The <code>.text-weight-normal</code> and <code>.text-weight-bold</code> classes allow you to override an element's font weight.</p>
      <pre><code>&lt;p>This is a regular paragraph.&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="text-weight-bold">This is a bold paragraph.&lt;/p>
&lt;h4>This is a regular h4.&lt;/h4>
